<div class="row">
  <div class="span4">
    <div class="carousel-tot">
      <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide">
        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
        </ol>
        <!-- Carousel items -->
        <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="active item"><%= image_tag("carousel1.gif") %></div>
        <div class="item"><%= image_tag("carousel2.gif") %></div>
        <div class="item"><%= image_tag("carousel3.gif") %></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div> 
  </div>


  <div class="span8">
    <%= link_to "mooseum", root_path, class: 'logo' %>
  	<p class="description1">Learn the secrets of the still life</p>
  	<p class="description2">Get the Audioguide for museum and start your journey in time!</p>
  	<p>
  		<%= image_tag("googleplay.png", alt: "Googleplay Image", id:"googleplay") %>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row background-down">
  <div class="span12">
    <div class="row title-step">
      <div class="span12 text-center">
        <p>Discover the mistery of ancient world </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row step1">
          <div class="span8 offset4">
            <h1>SCAN!</h1>
            <p>In each compatible museum you can find a QR code printed next to the exibit. You can easily open Mooseum app and scan the code. </p>
          </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row step2">
      <div class="span8 offset4">
        <h1>LISTEN!</h1>
        <p>After you scan the code you can listen to the exibit description and find out more informations about it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row step3">
      <div class="span8 offset4">
        <h1>LEARN MORE ABOUT IT!</h1>
        <p>This is a great app to learn more in a new interactional way!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
